reviews.text: Food quality is good at a slightly higher price. For their special food items. Preordering 24 hours ahead is required.

Some dishes were still keeping its standard. Overall a bit pricy for the food. Special order of cause were amazing and delicious still. Portion was not big enough, end up we need to order some more in order to fill up our stomach.
Good food, nice place and fair price
Salt baked chicken made in the most traditional way which you could hardly find in other places of Hong Kong.
Very nice and clean place, very nice staff. I can recommend the BBQ pork appetizer and the pork belly with squid.

reviews.text: 食物一流👏
值得推荐的精致傳統粵菜。店里裝修明亮新式，座位舒適，服务细心周到。我们一共点了8道菜，每道都十分出色，用料新鲜，味道，火候控制得刚刚好。觉得他的煙燻鸡最美味，鸡肉够嫩煙燻味浓。
Food quality is good at a slightly higher price. For their special food items. Preordering 24 hours ahead is required.

Some dishes were still keeping its standard. Overall a bit pricy for the food. Special order of cause were amazing and delicious still. Portion was not big enough, end up we need to order some more in order to fill up our stomach.
Good food, nice place and fair price
